    <title>The vertex ideal of a lattice</title>
    <summary>  We introduce a monomial ideal whose standard monomials encode the vertices of
all fibers of a lattice. We study the minimal generators, the radical, the
associated primes and the primary decomposition of this ideal, as well as its
relation to initial ideals of lattice ideals.
</summary>
